parsed caption:
Die Gläserne Manufaktur in Dresden ist eine von drei Produktionsstätten der
Volkswagen Sachsen GmbH. In Dresden wurde von 2002 bis 2016 der Phaeton
produziert, seit April 2017 der Elektro-Golf der Marke Volkswagen. Zugleich
entwickelt sich die Manufaktur zum Center of Future Mobility. Mitte 2018 waren
am Standort 380 Personen beschäftigt.

description: ['kitchen cabinet and contents, which escaped destruction during 2022 Ruisian atatcks on Borodyanka']
parsed caption:
[Borodianka](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Borodianka "en:Borodianka")
settlement (Kyiv Oblast of Ukraine) after Russian shelling. [Emergency Service
of Ukraine](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/State_Emergency_Service_of_Ukraine
"en:State Emergency Service of Ukraine") removes rubble and searches people
who can remain underneath. The first day of the work.  
In the right, a kitchen cabinet with a [ceramic
cock](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vasylkiv_maiolica_rooster "en:Vasylkiv
maiolica rooster") is seen, which became a meme and a symbol of persistence
against Russian invasion. On 14 April, this cabinet was transferred to Museum
of the Revolution of Dignity ([an
article](https://web.archive.org/web/20220417103803/https://life.pravda.com.ua/culture/2022/04/17/248281/)).

description: ['star at the centre of the Solar System']
parsed caption:
AIA 1600 channel (as well as AIA 1700) often shows a web-like pattern of
bright areas that highlight places where bundles of magnetic fields lines are
concentrated. However, small areas with a lot of field lines will appear
black, usually near sunspots and active regions.  
  
**Where:** Transition region and upper photosphere

**Wavelength:** 1600 angstroms (0.00000016 m) = Far Ultraviolet

**Primary ions seen:** thrice ionized carbon (C IV) and Continuum

**Characteristic temperatures:** 6,000 K (11,000 F), and 100,000 K (180,000 F)

file_name: File:Sony Open in Hawaii - 2018 - Jerry Kelly (25767950478).jpg
parsed caption:
The 2018 Sony Open in Hawaii is a professional golf tournament on the PGA
Tour, and is part of the tour's FedEx Cup Series. It is contested at the
Waialae Country Club in Honolulu, Hawaii. Soldiers of the 8th Theater
Sustainment Command, including the 8th Military Police Brigade and 130th
Engineer Brigade, had the opportunity to caddie the 18th hole for the Sony
Open in Honolulu Jan. 10, 2018 at the Waialae Country Club as part of the
Birdies for the Brave program.

(Traditional **Radical 101**) in [order.gif

"Category:Order.gif stroke order images").  
This image is part of the [Commons:Stroke Order
Project](//commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Commons:Stroke_Order_Project
"Commons:Stroke Order
Project")([zh](//commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Commons:CJK_stroke_order_project/zh
"Commons:CJK stroke order
project/zh")-[de](//commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Commons:CJK_stroke_order_project/de
"Commons:CJK stroke order
project/de")-[ja](//commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Commons:CJK_stroke_order_project/ja
"Commons:CJK stroke order project/ja")), a project to create a complete set of
images depicting the right stroke order
([Protocols](//commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Commons:CJK_stroke_order:Protocols
"Commons:CJK stroke order:Protocols")).  
The [214 Kangxi
radicals](https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Commons:CJK_stroke_order:214_radicals)
have been completed by hand. The next goal is to complete the missing
animations from the page:
[GIF_progress](https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Commons:Stroke_Order_Project/Kanji_progress/GIF_progress).
Help is welcome, on this
[link](https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Commons:Stroke_Order_Project/Graphics_guidelines/Bitmap_animations_using_GIMP)
are the official guidelines.

file_name: File:The Women of World War II Cenotaph - geograph.org.uk - 1380084.jpg
depicts: ['Monument to the Women of World War II']
description: ['British national war memorial situated on Whitehall in London, UK']
parsed caption:
The Women of World War II Cenotaph The second cenotaph on Whitehall Gardens is
that commemorating the Women of World War II. I'm unsure if this is located in
TQ3079 or TQ3080, but my estimate is that it is just inside the top edge of
the former. Please feel free to correct me if I'm wrong. As you can see, there
is extensive roadworks happening along the whole length of Whitehall Gardens -
apparently this is due to some kind of new regeneration scheme, including new
cycling facilities and improved streetlighting, according to a nearby sign.
View taken looking north-northeast.

file_name: File:Wainwright Tomb, Bellefontaine Cemetery, St. Louis, MO - 53052516818.jpg
description: ['United States Historic Place in St. Louis, Missouri']
parsed caption:
Built in 1892, this Sullivanesque and Chicago School-style mausoleum was
designed by Louis Sullivan for Charlotte Dickson Wainwright, and her husband,
Ellis Wainwright, a brewery owner, who had commissioned Sullivan to design the
Wainwright Building in Downtown St. Louis, which was completed around the same
time as Charlotte’s death. The tomb is a small, yet graceful structure, which
evokes the tragic beauty of the life and death of Charlotte Dickson Wainwright
(1857-1891), whom died at the age of 34, and was noted in St. Louis social
circles for her beauty. Ellis Wainwright joined Charlotte in the tomb upon his
death in 1924 at the age of 74. The tomb features a limestone-clad exterior
with bands of Sullivanesque carved trim surrounding the windows and doors, and
framing the top of the elevations, with copper doors, a domed roof, a front
terrace flanked by piers, and copper screens at the window openings on the
side facades. The tomb was listed on the National Register of Historic Places
in 1970, and was designated a St. Louis Landmark in 1971. Today, the tomb is
widely regarded as the best mausoleum designed by Sullivan, and is the most
architecturally significant structure in historic Bellefontaine Cemetery on
the north side of St. Louis.

Today, the tomb is widely regarded as the best mausoleum designed by Sullivan, and is the most architecturally significant structure in historic Bellefontaine Cemetery on the north side of St. Louis.', 'source': 'commons-desc-page'}, 'DateTimeOriginal': {'value': '2023-03-23 12:47:27', 'source': 'commons-desc-page'}, 'Credit': {'value': 'https://www.flickr.com/photos/59081381@N03/53052516818/', 'source': 'commons-desc-page'}, 'Artist': {'value': 'w_lemay', 'source': 'commons-desc-page'}, 'LicenseShortName': {'value': 'CC BY-SA 2.0', 'source': 'commons-desc-page', 'hidden': ''}, 'UsageTerms': {'value': 'Creative Commons Attribution-Share Alike 2.0', 'source': 'commons-desc-page'}, 'AttributionRequired': {'value': 'true', 'source': 'commons-desc-page', 'hidden': ''}, 'LicenseUrl': {'value': 'https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0', 'source': 'commons-desc-page'}, 'Copyrighted': {'value': 'True', 'source': 'commons-desc-page', 'hidden': ''}, 'Restrictions': {'value': '', 'source': 'commons-desc-page', 'hidden': ''}, 'License': {'value': 'cc-by-sa-2.0', 'source': 'commons-templates', 'hidden': ''}}

file_name: File:Billie Piper at Brussels Comic Con 2019 12-27-29 ILCE-6500 DSC00829 (47304529031).jpg
parsed caption:
Comiccon Brussels - 2019 - Day 2 - Billie Piper

Our next guest is best known as Rose Tyler, the companion to the
ninth(Christopher Eccleston) and tenth(David Tennant) incarnation of The
Doctor in the BBC hit series DOCTOR WHO! We are of course talking about the
multi talented BILLIE PIPER(UK) ! Billie was at the basis of the Doctor Who
revival and was one of the actors who made the show have a renewed success.
More recently, Billie Piper was seen as a regular on the Showtime horror
series Penny Dreadful as Brona Croft, an Irish immigrant with a mysterious
past. Billie is an incredibly multi faceted entertainment professional as she
not only shines out as an actress, but also as a singer, dance and general
star of the stage and screen!

    
    
    ( FINALLY FOR THE FIRST TIME IN THE HEART OF EUROPE!
    

You will find us at the beautiful Tour & Taxis site near the Brussels North
train station. At Comic Con Brussels you will find Dealers, Artists, Actors,
... It's a Con that brings together all the things you love: MOVIES, GAMING,
COMICS, MANGA, COLLECTIBLES, ANIME, TV, CLOTHING, TOYS AND GADGETS AND A LOT
MORE!

Hope to see you there! We will have a blast! )

parsed caption:
A bronze memorial plaque on the building in Prague 4 Nusle (Horní 1466/10, 140
00 Praha 4 - Nusle) points out that in this building (in the apartment of
Marie and František Mandík) (since the beginning of occupation) were hiding
illegal resistance fighters. Representatives of illegal Organisations:
Defending the Nation (ON) and ÚVOD worked here and they held several meetings
here. For example here petered General Bedřich Homola or Colonel Josef
Churavý. The memorial plaque mentions two significant illegal workers from the
circle of the "Three Kings": Staff Captain Václav Morávek (* 1904 - 1942) and
the radio operator František Peltán (* 1913 - 1942). On 28 June 1941 Peltán's
illegal radio SPARTA II has been focused during transmitting from the flat of
spouses František and Marie Mandíks. František Peltán spiritedly escaped
arrest by the Gestapo in disguise for railroaders, but both husband and wife
were arrested. František Mandík was for resistance activities on October 3,
1941 executed.

Mid Devon : Tiverton Parkway Railway Station The station is linked to both
Tiverton and to Cullompton by hourly bus services that call at a bus stop in
the station car park. In addition to being situated close to the junction of
the M5 motorway and the A361 North Devon link road, the National Cycle Network
Route 3 (Bristol to Lands End) passes through the station and provides a safe
and quiet route to local towns.

description: ['Queer Bayreuth event in the city center']
parsed caption:
View of the Christopher Street Day in Bayreuth on 30.07.2022. It was the first
CSD in Bayreuth. It is assumed that there were 1500-2000 participants. The
event was peaceful. It started around 2 pm and went until after 4:30 pm.
During the event it rained several times. First there was a march through the
city center of Bayreuth, which ended in front of the tax office. There was a
rally with speeches by several people. The organizer was the association Queer
Bayreuth e.V. Here you can see demonstrators in the Opernstraße.

Coast Guard photo by Petty Officer 3rd Class Joel Guzman/Released)

file_name: File:Military Funeral Honors with Funeral Escort are Conducted for U.S. Marine Corps Maj. Gen. Harry Pickett in Section 52 - 53057934055.jpg
description: ['military cemetery in Arlington, Virginia, United States of America']
parsed caption:
Marines from the “The President’s Own” Marine Band and the Marine Barracks,
Washington, D.C. (8th and I) conduct military funeral honors with funeral
escort for U.S. Marine Corps Maj. Gen. Harry Pickett in Section 52 of
Arlington National Cemetery, Arlington, Va., July 19, 2023.

A WWI and WWII veteran, Pickett was the commanding officer at the Marine
Barracks Pearl Harbor when the Japanese attack on Dec. 7, 1941. He served for
31 years and was awarded the Legion of Merit.

Sandra Sharpe, Pickett’s granddaughter, received the U.S. flag from Pickett’s
service.

(U.S. Army photo by Elizabeth Fraser / Arlington National Cemetery / released)

commons_description:
{'DateTime': {'value': '2024-03-22 16:20:40', 'source': 'mediawiki-metadata', 'hidden': ''}, 'ObjectName': {'value': '2023-08-10 Sessão Especial - 17 Anos da Lei Maria da Penha, 03', 'source': 'mediawiki-metadata'}, 'CommonsMetadataExtension': {'value': 1.2, 'source': 'extension', 'hidden': ''}, 'Categories': {'value': 'Brazil photographs taken on 2023-08-10|Federal Senate of Brazil in August 2023|Flickr images missing SDC inception|Flickr images reviewed by FlickreviewR 2|Iza Arruda|Photographs by the Federal Senate of Brazil|Soraya Santos', 'source': 'commons-categories', 'hidden': ''}, 'Assessments': {'value': '', 'source': 'commons-categories', 'hidden': ''}, 'ImageDescription': {'value': 'Plenário do Senado Federal durante sessão especial destinada a celebrar o aniversário de 17 anos da Lei Maria da Penha, principal instrumento jurídico brasileiro de combate à violência doméstica.
A Lei Maria da Penha leva o nome da farmacêutica Maria da Penha Maia Fernandes, que ficou paraplégica após tentativa de feminicídio cometida pelo seu marido. Ele respondeu em liberdade e só foi preso 20 anos depois. O caso estimulou a apresentação de um projeto de lei sobre o tema, em 2004. O texto virou lei dois anos depois.
Mesa:
procuradora da Mulher da Câmara dos Deputados, deputada Soraya Santos (PL-RJ);
ministra de Estado das Mulheres, Cida Gonçalves;
requerente desta sessão, senadora Leila Barros (PDT-DF);
presidente do Senado Federal, senador Rodrigo Pacheco (PSD-MG);
assessor técnico da Secretaria-Geral da Mesa, Iago Ruas Almeida Pereira;
secretária-geral das Relações Exteriores, embaixadora Maria Laura Rocha;
1ª coordenadora adjunta da Bancada Feminina da Câmara dos Deputados, deputada Iza Arruda (MDB-PE);
líder da Bancada Feminina do Senado Federal, senadora Daniella Ribeiro (PSD-PB).
Foto: Pedro França/Agência Senado', 'source': 'commons-desc-page'}, 'DateTimeOriginal': {'value': '2023-08-10 15:43:28', 'source': 'commons-desc-page'}, 'Credit': {'value': 'https://www.flickr.com/photos/agenciasenado/53107300636/', 'source': 'commons-desc-page'}, 'Artist': {'value': 'Agência Senado', 'source': 'commons-desc-page'}, 'LicenseShortName': {'value': 'CC BY 2.0', 'source': 'commons-desc-page', 'hidden': ''}, 'UsageTerms': {'value': 'Creative Commons Attribution 2.0', 'source': 'commons-desc-page'}, 'AttributionRequired': {'value': 'true', 'source': 'commons-desc-page', 'hidden': ''}, 'LicenseUrl': {'value': 'https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0', 'source': 'commons-desc-page'}, 'Copyrighted': {'value': 'True', 'source': 'commons-desc-page', 'hidden': ''}, 'Restrictions': {'value': '', 'source': 'commons-desc-page', 'hidden': ''}, 'License': {'value': 'cc-by-2.0', 'source': 'commons-templates', 'hidden': ''}}

description: ['star at the centre of the Solar System']
parsed caption:
AIA 0193 channel highlights the outer atmosphere of the Sun - called the
corona - as well as hot flare plasma. Hot active regions, solar flares, and
coronal mass ejections will appear bright here. The dark areas - called
coronal holes - are places where very little radiation is emitted, yet are the
main source of solar wind particles.

**Where:** Corona and hot flare plasma

**Wavelength:** 193 angstroms (0.0000000193 m) = Extreme Ultraviolet

**Primary ions seen:** 11 times ionized iron (Fe XII)

commons_description:
{'DateTime': {'value': '2018-05-15 22:08:31', 'source': 'mediawiki-metadata', 'hidden': ''}, 'ObjectName': {'value': '319455 and 319 and 422 Bedford to Sevenoaks 2E19 (14925991023)', 'source': 'mediawiki-metadata'}, 'CommonsMetadataExtension': {'value': 1.2, 'source': 'extension', 'hidden': ''}, 'Categories': {'value': 'British Rail Class 319s in First Capital Connect Urban Lights livery|British Rail Class 319s of Govia Thameslink Railway|Flickr images reviewed by FlickreviewR 2|Train images uploaded by OceanAtoll', 'source': 'commons-categories', 'hidden': ''}, 'Assessments': {'value': '', 'source': 'commons-categories', 'hidden': ''}, 'ImageDescription': {'value': '

Class 319 dual-voltage electric multiple-unit (EMU) number 319455 built by BREL York in 1987 or 1988 works 2E19 from Bedford to Sevenoaks on 15 October 2014. From the start of the Govia Franchise (14 September 2014) 24% of Govia Thameslink Railway services were delayed between 12 October 2014 and the 8 November 2014. Between 9 November and 6 December 2014 this improved slightly with only 21.3% being delayed but a further 4% were cancelled. Govia attribute this to train failure of old and new rolling stock and infrastructure problems e.g. <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/99279135@N05/15583827068/">track circuit failure</a>, while the watchdog London TravelWatch were also concerned about the lack of train drivers e.g. "<a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/99279135@N05/14975418773/">an issue with the train crewe</a>" across the franchise. During the previous franchise First Capital Connect (FCC) had Alstoms TrainTracer on-board monitoring module added to the Train Control & Management System (TCMS) and Traction Control racks of all class 319s. This module monitors major components and reports data for developing faults and non-critical failures to a ground-based server for engineers to remotely analyse with maintenance management software and plan maintenance. GPS data collected also allows them to identify the precise location where a fault has occurred. Alstom claim that through this planned maintenance the amount of time trains are unavailable for use is reduced by 30%.

description: ['star at the centre of the Solar System']
parsed caption:
AIA 0193 channel highlights the outer atmosphere of the Sun - called the
corona - as well as hot flare plasma. Hot active regions, solar flares, and
coronal mass ejections will appear bright here. The dark areas - called
coronal holes - are places where very little radiation is emitted, yet are the
main source of solar wind particles.

**Where:** Corona and hot flare plasma

**Wavelength:** 193 angstroms (0.0000000193 m) = Extreme Ultraviolet

**Primary ions seen:** 11 times ionized iron (Fe XII)

**Characteristic temperature:** 1.25 million K (2.25 million F)

outer atmosphere of the Sun - the corona. Active regions, solar flares, and
coronal mass ejections will appear bright here. The dark areas - called
coronal holes - are places where very little radiation is emitted, yet are the
main source of solar wind particles.

**Where:** Active regions of the corona

**Wavelength:** 211 angstroms (0.0000000211 m) = Extreme Ultraviolet

**Primary ions seen:** 13 times ionized iron (Fe XIV)

**Characteristic temperature:** 2 million K (3.6 million F)

parsed caption:
The Porsche 356 was a lightweight luxury sports car built from 1948-65, rear
engine and rear wheel drive, available as a hardtop coupe or a cabriolet. It
was replaced by the 911 in 1963, but the 356 continued to be built until 1965
The first 356, 1948-54, had a split or centre crease in the windscreen. The
prototype was the 356-1 roadster, these 356-2 are the first production cars.
The 1955-59 356A got a one piece windscreen. Styling changed with the 1959-64
356B, it got a flatter hood, twin engine grilles and a larger back window. The
last 356, the 1964-65 356C, very similar to the B but the shape of the hood
was squarer at the bottom and it got disc brakes. Engine; 1.1 - 2.0 litre air
cooled flat 4 cyl (4 cam Carrera option from 1955)

Photographed at the Petersen Museum

description: ['star at the centre of the Solar System']
parsed caption:
AIA 0193 channel highlights the outer atmosphere of the Sun - called the
corona - as well as hot flare plasma. Hot active regions, solar flares, and
coronal mass ejections will appear bright here. The dark areas - called
coronal holes - are places where very little radiation is emitted, yet are the
main source of solar wind particles.  
  
**Where:** Corona and hot flare plasma

**Wavelength:** 193 angstroms (0.0000000193 m) = Extreme Ultraviolet

**Primary ions seen:** 11 times ionized iron (Fe XII)

**Characteristic temperature:** 1.25 million K (2.25 million F)

file_name: File:Smrk trojak v Lanech po vetrne bouri jizni kmen.jpg
description: ['genus of evergreen, coniferous tree', 'memorable tree in Plzeň-město District, Czech Republic']
parsed caption:
Jedná se o smrk ztepilý v lese Lány nedaleko Plzně.

Původní kmen se 2,5m nad zemí rozděloval na tři přímé kmeny. Od roku 1987 je
chráněn jako památný strom. Stáří stromu je odhadováno na 140 let, původní
výška kmenů je cca 38 m. Na vrcholu jedné z korun rostl legendami opředený
cizopasník čarověník. Strom byl poškozen patrně při větrné bouři dne
21.10.2021.

Fotografie zachycují stav stromu týden po jeho destrukci.

description: ['fourth crewed flight of the United States Apollo program']
parsed caption:
AS10-29-4289. The craters Maskelyne D and J are at left, and the crater
Wallach is in the distance. A group of ridges at left was informally called
_Bob's Bend_ by the astronauts. Part of the highlands in the foreground was
called _Barbara Mesa_.

portable commercial radar display, shortly after getting underway from a
10-day port visit to the Kingdom of
[en:Bahrain](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bahrain "en:Bahrain"). The crew
used the port visit as a working port to perform a mid-deployment upkeep.

John F. Kennedy \(CV-67\)") Carrier Strike Group (CSG) and is on deployment in

Die Tableaus mit Eisenbahnfahrkarten wurden von dem Sammler und Opernsänger
Fritz Hellmuth zwischen dem Ende des 19. Jahrhunderts bis ca. 1925 erstellt.
Hierfür sammelte er weltweit auf eigenen Reisen Fahrkarten oder ließ sich
diese von den Eisenbahngesellschaften zuschicken. Die Sammlung wurde 1926 vom
Berliner Verkehrs- und Baumuseum übernommen und ist heute im Historischen
Archiv der Stiftung Deutsches Technikmuseum Berlin zugänglich.

in an area of 640.72 km2. These photos were taken in the context of both [Wiki
Takes Itu](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/pt:Wikip%C3%A9dia:GLAM/Wiki_Ocupa_Itu
"w:pt:Wikipédia:GLAM/Wiki Ocupa Itu") and [Wiki Loves Monuments
2021](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/pt:Wikip%C3%A9dia:Wiki_Loves_Monuments_2021/Brasil
"w:pt:Wikipédia:Wiki Loves Monuments 2021/Brasil").

file_name: File:Secretary of Defense Lloyd J. Austin III greets Papua New Guinea Prime Minister James Marape in Port Moresby, Papua New Guinea, July 27, 2023 - 230727-D-TT977-0132.jpg
parsed caption:
Secretary of Defense Lloyd J. Austin III greets Papua New Guinea Prime
Minister James Marape in Port Moresby, Papua New Guinea, July 27, 2023. Austin
is the first ever sitting U.S. Secretary of Defense to visit the South Pacific
island to discuss next steps following the recent signature of the U.S.-Papua
New Guinea Defense Cooperation Agreement (DCA), which reflects the partnership
and shared values as Pacific countries, the importance of ensuring the
security and prosperity of the region, and our shared commitment to a free and
open Indo-Pacific.(DoD photo by Chad J. McNeeley)

description: ["large natural elevation of the Earth's surface"]
parsed caption:
Hallstatt is a village on Lake Hallstatt's western shore in Austria's
mountainous Salzkammergut region. Its 16th-century Alpine houses and alleyways
are home to cafes and shops. A funicular railway connects to Salzwelten, an
ancient salt mine with a subterranean salt lake, and to Skywalk Hallstatt
viewing platform. A trail leads to the Echern Valley glacier garden with
glacial potholes and Waldbachstrub Waterfall.

parsed caption:
Secretary of Defense Lloyd J. Austin III meets with personnel assigned to the
California Air National Guard 129th Rescue Wing at Moffett Federal Airfield,
Calif., Dec. 1, 2023. The wing’smission is to train and prepare to perform its
wartime mission of combat search and rescue anywhere in the world. The 129th
has performed a wide variety of civilian search and rescue missions, including
distressed persons aboard ships, lost or injured hikers, and medical
evacuations. (DoD photo by Chad J. McNeeley)

description: ['ticket confirming fare payment or other ground of admission right to train ride']
parsed caption:
Die Tableaus mit Eisenbahnfahrkarten wurden von dem Sammler und Opernsänger
Fritz Hellmuth zwischen dem Ende des 19. Jahrhunderts bis ca. 1925 erstellt.
Hierfür sammelte er weltweit auf eigenen Reisen Fahrkarten oder ließ sich
diese von den Eisenbahngesellschaften zuschicken. Die Sammlung wurde 1926 vom
Berliner Verkehrs- und Baumuseum übernommen und ist heute im Historischen

parsed caption:
Inside picnic area Green 2 at the south end of the main section of Cunningham
Park, at Aberdeen Road and 196th Place west of Francis Lewis Boulevard in
Fresh Meadows, Queens. The park's picnic areas were overhauled during the
[2018 renovations](https://www.nycgovparks.org/planning-and-building/capital-
project-tracker/project/6486) to the park, with new tables, paving and mulch.
It is much nicer than what I remember as a kid.

University campus, Cheyney, Pennsylvania, USA. Marker text reads, "Educator,
writer, humanist, missionary. A former slave, she graduated from Oberlin
College in 1865. Principal, Institute for Colored Youth, 1869-1902 (I.C.Y.
became Cheyney University, 1983). Coppin pioneered industrial arts and teacher
education."
